MODULE
     eva_sup  - A Supervisor for the EVA Application

DESCRIPTION
     This module provides a supervisor for the entire EVA  appli-
     cation. An application can use this supervisor, or write its
     own, using the _s_t_a_r_t__l_i_n_k functions of the  individual  ser-
     vices.

     The supervisor can be configured to start the different  EVA
